### PTY (Pseudo-Terminal) API Tests
### Tests for PtyController endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### OpenCode server: http://localhost:4096

### Get all PTY sessions
### Returns a list of all active PTY sessions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/pty
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create new PTY session
### Creates a new pseudo-terminal session
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pty/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "command": "/bin/bash",
  "rows": 24,
  "cols": 80,
  "cwd": "/project"
}

###

### Create PTY with different shell
### Creates a PTY session with a specific shell
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pty/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "command": "/bin/zsh",
  "rows": 30,
  "cols": 120,
  "cwd": "/home/user/project"
}

###

### Get specific PTY session
### Returns details of a specific PTY session
# @prompt id Replace with actual PTY session ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/pty/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Update PTY session
### Updates the size of a PTY session
# @prompt id Replace with actual PTY session ID
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/pty/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "size": {
    "rows": 40,
    "cols": 100
  }
}

###

### Write to PTY session
### Sends input to a PTY session
# @prompt id Replace with actual PTY session ID
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/pty/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": "ls -la\n"
}

###

### Delete PTY session
### Terminates and removes a PTY session
# @prompt id Replace with actual PTY session ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/pty/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

###
